com.anaplan.client.jdbc

Class JDBCCellReader

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.anaplan.client.jdbc.JDBCCellReader
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    CellReader

    public class JDBCCellReader
extends java.lang.Object
implements CellReader
    An implementation of CellReader that connects to a JDBC data source. A query is executed and the results are read one record at a time.
    Since:
    1.2
